{
  "texts": [
    "Instructional prompts were used to query the same information from all articles using OpenAI's GPT-3.5 Turbo (Fig. 1).",
    "A complete match between the 2 approaches was defined as accurate.",
    "Concordance for each information extraction was calculated as the number of articles with accurate information extracted by OpenAI's GPT-3.5 Turbo divided by the total number of articles.",
    "The time taken for extraction was also assessed.",
    "ResultsOf the twenty papers, GPT-3.5 Turbo was unable to extract information from three (15%) articles as they were not in PDF format."
  ]
}